column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z,   fsps.logMass, fsps.age, fsps.metallicity,   s.specobjid, s.class, s.z as redshift,   pz.z as photoz  FROM fGetNearbyObjEq(#,#,#) n  JOIN PhotoObj AS p on p.objid = n.objid  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = n.objid  JOIN PhotoZ AS pz ON pz.objid = n.objid  JOIN stellarMassFSPSGranWideDust as fsps ON s.specobjid =fsps.specobjid  WHERE   s.class = GALAXY
